        <div class="left-content">
          <h4>Our Journey</h4>
          <p>Welcome to our headquarters in Casablanca. Founded in 2010, our family-owned business has been driven by a strong passion for mechanical engineering and metallurgy. After years of growth and consolidation, we continue our development with determination, focused on providing high-quality solutions to our clients.</p>
          
          <p>We specialize in importing machines and equipment for mechanical machining—ranging from turning to milling, chip removal, sheet metal work, presses, tooling, and all aspects of the metallurgy industry. Our focus is on offering comprehensive solutions in the world of metallurgy.</p>

          <p>We import directly from Italy, selecting only high-quality, reliable products that meet the specific needs of the Moroccan market. Each machine is carefully inspected and serviced before delivery, ensuring that we provide a serious, transparent, and professional service to our clients.</p>

          <p>Customer satisfaction is at the heart of our philosophy. We take pride in hearing positive feedback about our work and our commitment to quality. Since our founding, we have expanded rapidly, and today we are a growing company with a promising future.</p>
